00:53:02,437 --> 00:53:27,310
I've been a lifelong resident of Medford, formerly living on Placid Road at my current address. I'm here tonight, not because I'm a business owner, nor I have a family member who owns a business in Medford. I am here because I have a strong interest in the financial prosperity and wellbeing of the local community.

